data.description: Discover the perfect blend of mid-century craftsman charm and county comfort in this well-kept, single-story gem nestled in Canby. You can't help but notice its immediate charm and beauty at first sight. The front porch is a jaw dropper. This gorgeous 3-bedroom 2 bath home has it all. Tons of storage space with cupboards galore. This beauty has a warm and inviting feel with special charm.  The Primary suite offers the ultimate in privacy and relaxation. With gorgeous natural lighting and very open floor plan. Wake up to sunrises and enjoy your morning coffee on the rear covered patio. The oversized kitchen has plenty of room for any occasion and storage to boot. With the stainless appliances, large sink and laundry right off the kitchen. Don't forget the bonus room above the detached garage, it would make a fantastic office, gym or playroom, you decide! Last but not least, bring the mini farm, this .92 of an acre lot has plenty of room for horses or other animals. Not to mention the convenient location, just a quick hop to Canby, Molalla or Oregon city. You won't want to miss this one. Schedule a tour today!
